nodes.text: Sally Guinness is a British actress who has an uncredited cameo as a Supreme Council member in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She is the granddaughter of Alec Guinness, who played Obi-Wan Kenobi in the original trilogy. She has worked on TV series such as Marcella, Black Mirror and Shallow Grave.
